commit.message:
properly express dependency of qhullcpp to qhullstatic_r (#128)

[From spacelm] This way consumers don't have to link Qhull::qhullstatic_r at all when their direct dependency is only Qhull::qhullcpp, transitive informations are carried by targets, which is what a user would expect from a CMake target.
